/span>\n    <table class=\"backgroundTable\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; width: 100%;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <table class=\"emailDisplayFullWidth\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\n            <tr>\n  <td class=\"emailTopBar\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" width=\"100%\" style=\"padding-top: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 30px; padding-left: 30px; border-bottom: 6px solid #eee; text-align: center;\">\n    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100%!important;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"color:#aeaeae;font-family:'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:1px;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;\" align=\"center\">\n          <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #3db249; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n            <font color=\"#aeaeae\">\n              <img label=\"Logo\" class=\"logo\" src=\"https://image.email.lookout.com/lib/fe9915707362077c70/m/1/lookout-logo.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Lookout Mobile Security Logo\" height=\"40\" width=\"200\" style=\"display: block; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border-width: 0;\" />\n            </font>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n\n           <tr>\n              <td height=\"15\">\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n  <td align=\"center\">\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\">\n          <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\nResearchers recently found a piece of iOS malware called XcodeGhost that has been embedded into a number of applications in the Apple App Store, without the app developers\u2019 knowledge. These unsuspecting apps include popular apps such as WeChat and CamCard.<br><br> \n\n<strong>What can XcodeGhost do?</strong><br>\nXcodeGhost is a piece of malware that can steal data and potentially trick people into providing their personally identifiable information. The XcodeGhost creators were able to repackage a tool used by legitimate iOS and OSX developers to create apps. When those developers created their apps using this tampered-with tool, they unknowingly inserted malware into their applications.<br><br>\n\nThe malware made it into several applications that were live in the Apple App Store.<br><br>\n\n<strong>Does Lookout protect me?</strong><br>\nWe are providing you with a <a class=\"green\" href=\"https://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=f3a2d0637875657796374fceb6dff38bc1ac73728c7f0ab271dc2181a37d9c2390d9a63f5a7b67e0\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: inherit; font-weight: bold; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #3db249;\">list of all affected applications</a> so you can remove them from your device immediately. Unfortunately, Apple has recently eliminated the ability for third party developers (like Lookout) to see which apps are running on your device, which limits our ability to alert you about malicious apps, but we will continue to update this list to make sure you have the most up-to-date information.<br><br>\n\n<strong>How do I protect my iOS devices?</strong><br>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"bullet-list\" style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\n    <table class=\"list-table\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 550px; border: 0;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bullet-green\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n          &#8226;\n        </td>\n        <td valign=\"bottom\" class=\"list-table-text\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n           Be aware of the applications pushing dialog boxes to your screen and don\u2019t enter personal information without first being aware of who is asking for it.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bullet-green\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n          &#8226;\n        </td>\n        <td valign=\"bottom\" class=\"list-table-text\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n         If you have any of the apps on your phone (listed on our blog), you should delete them immediately and wait until the app developer has released a new version with a patch.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bullet-green\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n          &#8226;\n        </td>\n        <td valign=\"bottom\" class=\"list-table-text\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">\n         If one of these apps is running on your device, we also recommend that you change your Apple account password and be wary of any suspicious  emails or push notifications to your device asking for personal information.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n          </font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            <tr>\n              <td height=\"10\">\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n<tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align\">\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"button-green\" style=\"display: inline-block; text-align: center; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 500; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: #3db249; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; min-width: 200px; width: 200px; max-width: 200px; margin: 10px 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #338f45;\">\n<a href=\"https://click.email.lookout.com/?qs=f3a2d063787565776ef3ef17bea8ba0053c8eac1092f3ae16b9fa8f8bf1d21d32bb4185733d1323a\" class=\"button-text\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; \">See the Impacted Apps</a>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n            <tr>\n              <td height=\"20\">\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n  <td align=\"center\">\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\"